atalà</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-cs"><a href="https://cs.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bertram_Brockhouse" title="Bertram Brockhouse — tchèque" lang="cs" hreflang="cs" class="interlanguage-link-target">Čeština</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-da"><a href="https://da.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bertram_N._Brockhouse" title="Bertram N. Brockhouse — danois" lang="da" hreflang="da" class="interlanguage-link-target">Dansk</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-de"><a href="https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bertram_Brockhouse" title="Bertram Brockhouse — allemand" lang="de" hreflang="de" class="interlanguage-link-target">Deutsch</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-en"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bertram_Brockhouse" title="Bertram Brockhouse — anglais" lang="en" hreflang="en" class="interlanguage-link-target">English</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-es"><a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bertram_Brockhouse" title="Bertram Brockhouse — espagnol" lang="es" hreflang="es" class="interlanguage-link-target">Español</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-et"><a href="https://et.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bertram_Brockhouse" title="Bertram Brockhouse — estonien" lang="et" hreflang="et" class="interlanguage-link-target">Eesti</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-eu"><a href="https://eu.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bertram_Brockhouse" title="Bertram Brockhouse — basque" lang="eu" hreflang="eu" class="interlanguage-link-target">Euskara</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-fa"><a href="https://fa.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D8%A8%D8%B1%D8%AA%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%85_%D8%A8%D8%B1%DA%A9%D9%87%D8%A7%D9%88%D8%B3" title="برترام برکهاوس — persan" lang="fa" hreflang="fa" class="interlanguage-link-target">فارسی</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-fi"><a href="https://fi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bertram_Brockhouse" title="Bertram Brockhouse — finnois" lang="fi" hreflang="fi" class="interlanguage-link-target">Suomi</a></li><li c